import React from "react";
import { Code, Database, BookOpen } from "react-feather";
import {
  Card,
  Box,
  Button,
  Image,
  Stack,
  Set,
  Heading,
  Container,
  Columns,
  Text,
  Paragraph,
  Badge,
} from "bumbag";

const Skills = () => (
  <Container padding="2rem 1rem">
    <Heading use="h4" marginBottom="major-4">
      Skills
    </Heading>

    <Set spacing="major-4">
      {/* <Box> */}
      <Card altitude="400" textAlign="left">
        <Code color="#5863D8" />
        <Heading
          use="h4"
          fontWeight="semibold"
          paddingTop="1.5rem"
          paddingBottom="1.5rem"
          cursor='pointer'
          onHo
        >
          Languages
        </Heading>
        <Set orientation="vertical" spacing="major-2">
          <Paragraph color="secondary" fontSize="200">Java</Paragraph>
          <Paragraph color="secondary" fontSize="200">JavaScript</Paragraph>
          <Paragraph color="secondary" fontSize="200">C++</Paragraph>
        </Set>
      </Card>
      {/* </Box> */}

      {/* <Box> */}
      <Card altitude="400" textAlign="left">
        <Database color="#5863D8" />
        <Heading
          use="h4"
          fontWeight="semibold"
          paddingTop="1.5rem"
          paddingBottom="1.5rem"
        >
          Database
        </Heading>
        <Set orientation="vertical" spacing="major-2">
          <Paragraph color="secondary" fontSize="200">SQL Server</Paragraph>
          <Paragraph color="secondary" fontSize="200">MySQL</Paragraph>
          <Paragraph color="secondary" fontSize="200">MongoDB</Paragraph>
        </Set>
      </Card>
      {/* </Box> */}

      {/* <Box> */}
      <Card altitude="400" textAlign="left">
        <BookOpen color="#5863D8" />
        <Heading
          use="h4"
          fontWeight="semibold"
          paddingTop="1.5rem"
          paddingBottom="1.5rem"
        >
          Libraries
        </Heading>
        <Set orientation="vertical" spacing="major-2">
          <Paragraph color="secondary" fontSize="200">React.js</Paragraph>
          <Paragraph color="secondary" fontSize="200">Node.js</Paragraph>
          <Paragraph color="secondary" fontSize="200">Spring.java</Paragraph>
        </Set>
      </Card>
      {/* </Box> */}
      {/* <Paragraph>I've been learning to code about 2</Paragraph> */}
    </Set>
  </Container>
);

export default Skills;
